==问题和争议==
===預算超標===
康百世卡系統最初的安裝預算为1億7100萬加元，但目前的花費已經達到1億9400萬加元。2013年10月，運輸聯線承認，由於不可抗力的原因，加上通脹的影響，康百世卡系統將會超支達2300萬加元<ref>{{cite web|title=Compass Card upgrade costing extra $23 million: TransLink|url=http://bc.ctvnews.ca/compass-card-upgrade-costing-extra-23-million-translink-1.1493277|publisher=CTV British Columbia|accessdate=3 January 2014|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320185653/https://bc.ctvnews.ca/compass-card-upgrade-costing-extra-23-million-translink-1.1493277|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===新舊系統无法兼容===
2013年，[[素里|素里]]當地媒體《Surrey Leader》报道称：乘客如果在巴士上购买车票，巴士發出的轉車无法通过架空列车车站的闸门，只能用康百世卡才能通过<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.surreyleader.com/news/219684161.html |title=''Bus-to-SkyTrain transfers costly without smart card'', ''Surrey Leader'', 2013-08-14 |access-date=2015-11-05 |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320185643/https://www.surreynowleader.com/news/bus-to-skytrain-transfers-costly-without-smart-card/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在架空列車站的舊式驗票機，可以读取到巴士發出的轉車票。運輸聯線称，如果要升級巴士車票系統，与康百世卡系統兼容，就要再追加2500萬撥款<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vancitybuzz.com/2013/08/skytrain-to-not-accept-bus-transfers-with-new-translink-compass-card/ |title="SKYTRAIN WILL NOT ACCEPT BUS TRANSFERS WITH NEW TRANSLINK COMPASS CARD", ''Vancity Buzz", 2013-08-14 |access-date=2015-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140909162621/http://www.vancitybuzz.com/2013/08/skytrain-to-not-accept-bus-transfers-with-new-translink-compass-card/ |archive-date=2014-09-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===收費系統漏洞===
2013年9月系統測試期間，測試員發現一個嚴重漏洞：由於巴士上面無閘門，持有康百世卡的乘客可以靠提前刷卡不提前下车的方式，以一個收費區的票價乘坐三個收費區的车<ref>{{cite web|title=TransLink testers find Compass Card fare evasion loophole|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/translink-testers-find-compass-card-fare-evasion-loophole-1.2074337|publisher=CBC News|access-date=2015-11-05|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320185650/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/translink-testers-find-compass-card-fare-evasion-loophole-1.2074337|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因此，在2015進入全面使用階段，所有巴士一律按一個收費區收費。

===對殘疾用戶的不利和漏洞===
如果用戶有殘疾，使他們不能刷卡（特別是架空列車），殘疾用戶便不可以用公共交通。運輸聯線的臨時解決方案是派服務員協助殘疾用戶，或把殘疾用出入閘保持開啟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://globalnews.ca/news/2438633/translink-keeping-compass-card-gates-open-for-paralyzed-users/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-05-18 |archive-date=2022-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220130001304/https://globalnews.ca/news/2438633/translink-keeping-compass-card-gates-open-for-paralyzed-users/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/translink-sets-deadline-for-making-fare-gates-accessible/article29640376/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-05-18 |archive-date=2021-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201004601/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/translink-sets-deadline-for-making-fare-gates-accessible/article29640376/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

